query:
SELECT 
  o.orderNumber,
  o.orderDate,
  o.itemsCount as itens_no_pedido,
  COUNT(s.id) as itens_salvos_sales
FROM orders o
LEFT JOIN sales s ON o.blingId = s.blingOrderId
WHERE o.orderDate >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 12 MONTH)
  AND o.itemsCount > 0
GROUP BY o.id, o.orderNumber, o.orderDate, o.itemsCount
HAVING itens_salvos_sales = 0
LIMIT 10
